**INTUITIVE DESIGN**

YES.

It allows the user to be able to navigate through the app without any confusion, with the natural flow from top to bottom aligning with the users expectations.

**CONTENT PRIOITIZATION**

YES.

Only the necessary essential content was added, not too little or too much content was added.

**LEGIBLE TEXT CONTENT**

YES.

I made use of clear and readable font and sizes for the user to be able to read and understand the content displayed in the application.

**MAKE INTERFACE ELEMENTS CLEARLY VISIBLE**

YES.

The user can clearly see all the components on the screen. It is well spaced, not to crowded and doesnt have too much space between them.

**HAND POSITION CONTROLS**

YES.

The buttons are placed in a position where the user will be able to reach.
